OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA pleasant
OL,6,Fevening with widespread sunshine and
OL,7,Feasing winds for many, followed by a
OL,8,Fmostly clear and cool night, with a
OL,9,Flittle patchy cloud during the early
OL,10,Fhours. A gentle breeze throughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy start in the west,
OL,13,Fthen sunny. Otherwise, dry with sunny
OL,14,Fspells until late afternoon when it
OL,15,Fwill turn cloudier with a chance if
OL,16,Fsome light rain. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
